snippet.title: DZ & Riggy vs the World(s) II - World Update & Planned Release Window
snippet.description:
A look at ALMOST everything that's been completed in DZ & Riggy vs the World(s) II so far. I also plan on finishing this near the end of spring, so aiming for a May/June release. Of course, the game will wind up in the hands of DZ and Riggy first for streaming purposes before everybody else can get their hands on it!

You can follow ALL updates on this project in the #dz-and-riggy-vs-the-worlds-2 channel on DZ and Riggy's Discord server!

DZ & Riggy vs the World(s) II  on itch.io: https://uprc.itch.io/dzriggy2

See more DZ & Riggy vs the World(s) II videos here: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLDm3Ufb_Ohkid25hi-2jzkkiBPq9ZLXDI
